---
// AboutUs component for the AI workshop
---

<section id="about-us" class="section about-us">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-us-heading" data-aos="fade-up">
      <h2>Om Os</h2>
      <p>Projekt AI Workshop er et joint venture mellem erfarne erhvervsledere og teknologieksperter. Formålet er at støtte Danske virksomheder bedst muligt i en tid under stor forandring.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="team-grid" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
      <div class="team-member">
        <div class="member-image">
          <img 
            src="https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/C4E03AQFXvHsEcj_CHw/profile-displayphoto-shrink_400_400/profile-displayphoto-shrink_400_400/0/1516230884170?e=1752105600&v=beta&t=Y9bp0lbN3QTS7znoTNv6zBkfI4Q4HIXOh1kFVX1Zqjo"
            alt="Lars Kolind"
            width="300"
            height="300"
            style="filter: grayscale(100%) contrast(120%);"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="member-info">
          <h3>Lars Kolind</h3>
          <p class="member-title">Serial Entrepreneur</p>
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/larskolind/" class="linkedin-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M16 8a6 6 0 0 1 6 6v7h-4v-7a2 2 0 0 0-2-2 2 2 0 0 0-2 2v7h-4v-7a6 6 0 0 1 6-6z"></path>
              <rect x="2" y="9" width="4" height="12"></rect>
              <circle cx="4" cy="4" r="2"></circle>
            </svg>
            <span>LinkedIn Profil</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="team-member">
        <div class="member-image">
          <img 
            src="https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D4D03AQHItuCR-wbplg/profile-displayphoto-shrink_400_400/B4DZXrT9MMHwAg-/0/1743409632410?e=1752105600&v=beta&t=51yWoU9BmM5yx-4rmLx3guz_7YE7vFqwlFJPo6pjMFQ"
            alt="Frits Lyneborg"
            width="300"
            height="300"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="member-info">
          <h3>Frits Lyneborg</h3>
          <p class="member-title">Technologist</p>
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/frits-lyneborg/" class="linkedin-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M16 8a6 6 0 0 1 6 6v7h-4v-7a2 2 0 0 0-2-2 2 2 0 0 0-2 2v7h-4v-7a6 6 0 0 1 6-6z"></path>
              <rect x="2" y="9" width="4" height="12"></rect>
              <circle cx="4" cy="4" r="2"></circle>
            </svg>
            <span>LinkedIn Profil</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="about-us-text" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
      <p>
        Projekt AI Workshop er opstået som et joint venture mellem serial entrepreneur Lars Kolind 
        og technologist Frits Lyneborg, sammen med et netværk af erfarne erhvervsledere og teknologieksperter.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-us {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--color-gray-50) 0%, var(--color-white) 100%);
  }

  .about-us-heading {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  .about-us-heading h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--color-gray-900);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }

  .about-us-heading p {
    color: var(--color-gray-600);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .team-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-6);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  .team-member {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .member-image {
    width: 200px;
    height: 200px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-4);
    border-radius: 50%;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
  }

  .member-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .team-member:hover .member-image img {
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }

  .member-info h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-gray-900);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }

  .member-title {
    color: var(--color-gray-600);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }

  .linkedin-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    padding: var(--space-2) var(--space-3);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    background-color: var(--color-gray-100);
    color: var(--color-gray-700);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .linkedin-link:hover {
    background-color: var(--color-primary);
    color: var(--color-white);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .about-us-text {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--color-gray-700);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .team-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: var(--space-8);
    }

    .member-image {
      width: 250px;
      height: 250px;
    }
  }
</style>